      <h2>香港富商在台绑架案 警方怀疑港人指使犯案(图)</h2> 
     </div> 
     <div class="zw"> 
      <script type="text/javascript">showbd('2_3');</script> 
      <table width="630" border="0" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0" bgcolor="#f8f8f8">
